          <br>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary debt-btn" id="debt-goal">Select Goal</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-footer text-center my-4 debt">
        <div class="card">
        <p class="gCard">Getting out of debt is an important financial goal. Here are some tips to help you become debt-free:</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="debt">
          <li>Create a budget and track your spending</li>
          <li>Focus on paying off high-interest debt first</li>
          <li>Consider a balance transfer credit card to consolidate debt</li>
          <li>Explore debt counseling or debt consolidation programs</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>

<a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary back-btn">Return to Dashboard</a>
